Beacon & Unproto.help:
Sets up to 4 beacon text buffers.

Enter BLT, then at prompts:
  >>1 {beacon text 1}
  >>2 {beacon text 2}
  >>3 {beacon text 3}
  >>4 {beacon text 4}
  >>LTP (list transmission periods)
  >>1 EVERY hh:mm:ss
  >>2 AFTER hh:mm:ss STARTING AT hh:mm:ss

Allows multiple rotating beacons with different schedules.
